streams-related packages, so the coupling map in `research.md` flags a 
divergence that needs confirmation before slicing transport integration.\n5. 
**Telemetry naming**: 5d1 conventions are not yet landed on this branch; the 
span/event vocabulary proposed here may need realignment when 5d1 
merges.\n\nREADY FOR PLAN-EVAL.\n"}

